Package: natverse
Type: Package
Title: Install all NeuroAnatomy Toolbox packages
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person("Gregory","Jefferis", email="jefferis@gmail.com", 
    role = c("aut"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-0587-9355")),
    person("Sridhar","Jagannathan", email="j.sridharrajan@gmail.com", 
    role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-2078-1145")))
Description: Provides functionality for installing and updating all nat packages and friends in one go. This includes
    both CRAN and github only packages. Other functionalities like checking conflicts are also provided. Inspired from
    tidyverse and dtupdate packages.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
